ācchidyeti balāt. bhavato gṛhītvā niṣkṛpo mṛtyus tava kāyaṃ gṛdhrebhyo dāsyati. tadāpi na kaścit pratikāro bhaviṣyati ity abhiprāyaḥ.

<commentary>syād etat—yady api evam, tathāpi bhaktāc chādanamātreṇāpi paripālanīya ity atrāha.

yadi nāma bhṛtyakarmakaraṇaṃ tathāpi tatrānavasthāyisvabhāve vicakṣaṇo jñātvaiva pravartate, evaṃ prakṛte 'pi taddharmiṇi kenābhiprāyeṇa he manaḥ, tvaṃ kuruṣe vyayam upakaraṇopakṣayam?</commentary>

tat kiṃ sarvathaiva niravakāśo 'yaṃ kartavyaḥ? nety āha. vetanaṃ karmamūlyam.